The paper introduces a novel concept for learning parameters in a neural network, which is a fundamental topic in machine learning. The paper discusses the use of nonlinear transforms to model the network representations and achieve target-specific representations at the last network node. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
